Wed Apr 26 10:31:03 2000  Marcin Wolinski  <wolinski@mimuw.edu.pl>

	* mwcls.dtx: Nowe nazwy szablonów:
		\FormatBlockHeading
		\FormatHangHeading
		\FormatChapterHeading
		\FormatRunInHeading

	* mwcls.dtx: \DeclareSectioningCommand[flags]{cmd name}{level}
		{preskip}
		{head}
		{postskip}

	Flags (comma separated):
		runin - like \paragraph
		breakbefore - forced page break before
		breakafter - ditto after
		wholewidth - spans both columns when in twocolumn

	<postskip> is horizontal for run-in headings, vertical for others

	In the <head> argument:
		\ifHeadingNumbered - true iff heading has a number
		\HeadingText - is the heading text
		\HeadingRHeadText - text for running head
		\HeadingTOCText - text for TOC

